                    And contrast is the truth of what the world is made of<br>
                    Movement and stillness, inhale and exhale, inside and outside, birth and death, the begining and the end ...
                p.
                    I interact with myself through the action of tapping and knocking.<br>
                    I acquaint myself through the mirror image reflected in metal.<br>
                    I live with the laws of nature through the harmonically multiplied audio.
                p.
                    The spaceship-like drum,<br>
